        "type": "prov:Entity",
        "name": "Synthesis of prior pedicle screw biomechanical studies informing model priors",
        "rdfs:comment": "A comprehensive synthesis aggregating findings from twelve peer-reviewed studies published between 2008 and 2022 on pedicle screw construct mechanics under compression-bending. The synthesis establishes prior distributions for titanium alloy elastic modulus, screw-rod interface friction coefficients, and polyurethane foam block stiffness used as model inputs. It draws on cadaveric, synthetic bone, and in vitro data and was reviewed internally by the modeling team prior to model parameterization. The breadth of source material and the internal review process were considered sufficient to treat this synthesis as well-established background knowledge underpinning the model priors."
      }
